\paragraph{Step~C --- Read your first dashboard.}
Once logged in, the operator lands on the security dashboards populated by the
Filebeat Suricata module. The most immediately useful view is the
\emph{Top Alert Signatures} panel, which summarises what Suricata has been
detecting.

